div.font:
- Set ayanamsa to Lahiri ayanamsa in the Swiss Ephemeris
- Find sunrise time for the given place,
- Get Nirayana Longitude of the Moon by subtracting Ayanamsa from the Sayana Longitude of the Moon,
- Find the nakshatra by multiplying the obtained Nirayana longitude with 27 and dividing by 360,
- append the obtained nakshatra to the answer vector.
